info.interactivesystems.gamificationengine.entities.marketPlace

Class Bid

  • java.lang.Object
    • info.interactivesystems.gamificationengine.entities.marketPlace.Bid

  • @Entity
public class Bid
extends Object
    A player can give one or more bids for an offer so its total prize gets higher and in order to increase the incentive of fulfilling the task. The bidden amount of coins will be subtracted from the bidder’s current account and will be added to the offer’s current prize. Each player can make several bids on condition that her/his coins are enough otherwise the bid cannot be done.
